Description
-----------

The Ming Server is a lightweight cgi-based python wiki, based on Martin
Pool's old piki code.  We have broken the single file out into classes,
created a normal python module from them, added authentication and file
locks and a few other goodies.


Requirements
------------

Python 2.2 or greater.


Installation
------------

Refer to the included INSTALL file for quick installation instructions.


Documentation
-------------

None at this time.  The original piki file is included because we think
it should be.
